  "text": "In case \u0393 = \u0393 \u2206 , the parameters p i are natural occupation numbers of \u2206 and the vectors f i are natural orbitals of \u2206, as can be seen by comparing (16) and [CITATION_1] . In this case, it follows from (23) that",
